WEBVTT

00:00.934 --> 00:02.265
If you want to get Knight...

00:02.335 --> 00:04.963
you have to deal with that
car of his at the same time.

00:05.038 --> 00:06.938
Okay, pal,
super pursuit mode.

00:13.046 --> 00:14.741
Julian, he took the bait.

00:14.881 --> 00:16.075
Michael, help.

00:16.149 --> 00:19.277
Okay, I'm on my way. You
better turbo-boost out of there.

00:19.419 --> 00:21.353
Michael, I'm in trouble.

00:21.621 --> 00:24.021
Now they got KITT.
I'm the one they want here!

00:24.090 --> 00:26.854
Open up, Knight,
or I kill the girl.

00:26.993 --> 00:28.688
No, Michael,
don't do it!

